{
  "_comment": "PLACEHOLDER. After Part A of onboarding/gsuite-setup.md, save the downloaded Desktop OAuth client here as oauth_client.json (without .example) and commit it. A Desktop OAuth key is non-confidential by Google's design, so committing it to this private repo is fine — and it's what lets the whole team get it on pull (onboarding = just `gs.py login`). Personal tokens are never committed (~/.shikshalokam/).",
